# NetMonitor-2.0 — Environment Variables
#
# This project does NOT require any environment variables for local development.
# All configuration is handled through:
#   - Info.plist (bundle configuration)
#   - project.yml → XcodeGen → .xcodeproj (build settings)
#   - AppSettings (runtime user preferences, UserDefaults-backed)
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Development Tool Requirements (not env vars, but required)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# brew install xcodegen       # Project file generation from project.yml
# brew install swiftlint      # Linting (enforced in pre-commit hook + CI)
# brew install swiftformat    # Formatting (enforced in pre-commit hook + CI)
# pip install bd              # Beads issue tracker (bd onboard to initialise)
#
# After cloning:
#   scripts/hooks/install-hooks.sh   # Install git pre-commit hook
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CI / GitHub Actions
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# The following secrets must be set in GitHub repository settings
# if you fork this repo and want CI to work:
#
# GITHUB_TOKEN   — auto-provided by GitHub Actions (no setup needed)
#
# Optional (for future Sentry / analytics integration):
# SENTRY_DSN=
# SENTRY_ORG=
# SENTRY_PROJECT=
